    <div>
      <p begin="0.0s" xml:id="p0" end="0.334s" region="topLeft">Title: Saving General Yang<br />story: TGPGFA010511<br />lang: TRD<br />SOM: 10:00:00:00</p>
      <p begin="2.0s" xml:id="p1" end="3.209s" region="topRight" >楊延昭</p>
      <p begin="0.0s" xml:id="p2" end="3.359s"  region="topRight">違反家規，漠視家主命令</p>
      <p begin="3.725s" xml:id="p3" end="5.684s">擅入招親擂台</p>
      <p begin="5.976s" xml:id="p4" end="7.725s">未盡兄長責任</p>
      <p begin="9.017s" xml:id="p5" end="11.809s">縱容楊延嗣魯莽行事</p>
      <p begin="12.517s" xml:id="p6" end="15.559s">楊延嗣，違反軍紀</p>
      <p begin="15.934s" xml:id="p7" end="19.559s">不顧家主命令，擂台爭鬥</p>
      <p begin="19.767s" xml:id="p8" end="23.725s">好勇逞強，全然不計後果</p>
      <p begin="24.224s" xml:id="p9" end="28.434s">二人所作所為，有損楊家威名</p>
      <p begin="28.934s" xml:id="p10" end="31.725s">各杖脊三十</p>
      <p begin="31.809s" xml:id="p11" end="33.184s">站好</p>
      <p begin="58.143s" xml:id="p12" end="59.059s">容兒</p>
      <p begin="59.851s" xml:id="p13" end="63.976s">你看天上的雲，像不像一群綿羊</p>
      <p begin="64.225s" xml:id="p14" end="68.224s">真的，大的雲就像大羊一樣</p>
      <p begin="68.475s" xml:id="p15" end="70.892s">旁邊跟著的就是小羊</p>
      <p begin="73.017s" xml:id="p16" end="75.725s">將來我也要養一群羊</p>
      <p begin="78.35s" xml:id="p17" end="80.517s">怎麼了？你想養羊？</p>
      <p begin="82.517s" xml:id="p18" end="84.434s">我要讓他們圍著我玩</p>
      <p begin="84.976s" xml:id="p19" end="89.143s">一手抱一個，背上還背著兩個</p>
      <p begin="89.475s" xml:id="p20" end="91.143s">地上還圍著四個</p>
      <p begin="92.767s" xml:id="p21" end="94.6s">到時候你一定要幫我</p>
      <p begin="94.642s" xml:id="p22" end="97.224s">怎麼幫你？幫你養羊？</p>
      <p begin="97.35s" xml:id="p23" end="99.434s">幫我當小羊們的楊媽媽</p>
      <p begin="106.392s" xml:id="p24" end="107.934s">這世上的人聽著</p>
      <p begin="108.143s" xml:id="p25" end="110.392s">當今大宋朝的柴郡主</p>
      <p begin="110.434s" xml:id="p26" end="112.934s">願意當楊媽媽了</p>
      <p begin="112.976s" xml:id="p27" end="115.6s">我願意當楊媽媽了</p>
      <p begin="116.851s" xml:id="p28" end="119.267s">爹，聖上預設擂台比武招親</p>
      <p begin="119.308s" xml:id="p29" end="120.6s">孩兒有絕對把握</p>
      <p begin="120.642s" xml:id="p30" end="122.224s">一定能將郡主娶回來</p>
      <p begin="122.517s" xml:id="p31" end="125.809s">延昭，你不得上擂台比武</p>
      <p begin="126.225s" xml:id="p32" end="128.434s">以後也不得再跟柴郡主交往</p>
      <p begin="128.475s" xml:id="p33" end="129.475s">為甚麼？</p>
      <p begin="129.934s" xml:id="p34" end="131.559s">潘國丈之子潘豹</p>
      <p begin="131.6s" xml:id="p35" end="133.184s">對柴郡主有意</p>
      <p begin="134.434s" xml:id="p36" end="136.6s">國丈向聖上獻策比武招親之時</p>
      <p begin="136.642s" xml:id="p37" end="138.059s">亦表明心意</p>
      <p begin="138.434s" xml:id="p38" end="139.767s">志在必得</p>
      <p begin="140.143s" xml:id="p39" end="142.059s">潘家一直對我楊家不滿</p>
      <p begin="142.101s" xml:id="p40" end="144.059s">你若前去跟潘豹比武</p>
      <p begin="144.225s" xml:id="p41" end="146.059s">必定加深兩家不和</p>
      <p begin="146.767s" xml:id="p42" end="148.725s">可我跟容兒自幼青梅竹馬，爹</p>
      <p begin="148.767s" xml:id="p43" end="150.684s">遼國對我大宋虎視眈眈</p>
      <p begin="150.725s" xml:id="p44" end="153.684s">正是需要潘、楊兩家同心抗敵之時</p>
      <p begin="153.809s" xml:id="p45" end="155.475s">豈能只顧及兒女私情</p>
      <p begin="155.517s" xml:id="p46" end="157.101s">爹…　　休要多言</p>
      <p begin="158.101s" xml:id="p47" end="160.517s">這是命令，退下吧</p>
      <p begin="161.517s" xml:id="p48" end="162.434s">去死吧</p>
      <p begin="164.725s" xml:id="p49" end="166.35s">技不如人，下臺</p>
      <p begin="168.224s" xml:id="p50" end="169.101s">潘豹</p>
      <p begin="169.6s" xml:id="p51" end="171.35s">靠暗器，就想奪人所愛？</p>
      <p begin="171.809s" xml:id="p52" end="173.642s">我就代六哥來教訓教訓你</p>
      <p begin="198.101s" xml:id="p53" end="199.017s">六哥</p>
      <p begin="219.559s" xml:id="p54" end="221.725s">娘…</p>
      <p begin="223.059s" xml:id="p55" end="224.059s">排風</p>
      <p begin="224.934s" xml:id="p56" end="225.809s">夫人</p>
      <p begin="226.225s" xml:id="p57" end="227.809s">給令公送去</p>
      <p begin="229.225s" xml:id="p58" end="230.143s">是</p>
      <p begin="236.934s" xml:id="p59" end="238.059s">聖上</p>
      <p begin="238.934s" xml:id="p60" end="242.725s">楊業縱子行兇，謀殺當今國舅</p>
      <p begin="242.767s" xml:id="p61" end="244.35s">罪大惡極</p>
      <p begin="245.059s" xml:id="p62" end="250.267s">臣妾懇請聖上判處楊家滿門抄斬</p>
      <p begin="250.892s" xml:id="p63" end="254.017s">以祭慰臣弟的在天之靈</p>
      <p begin="254.143s" xml:id="p64" end="255.475s">潘豹是自己跌死的</p>
      <p begin="255.517s" xml:id="p65" end="257.059s">怎能亂斬我楊家人？</p>
      <p begin="257.143s" xml:id="p66" end="258.059s">住口</p>
      <p begin="258.143s" xml:id="p67" end="259.184s">聖上</p>
      <p begin="259.6s" xml:id="p68" end="262.642s">豹兒自幼與臣妾形影不離</p>
      <p begin="262.892s" xml:id="p69" end="265.725s">是臣妾最疼愛的弟弟</p>
      <p begin="266.392s" xml:id="p70" end="269.434s">他年紀輕輕，胸懷大志</p>
      <p begin="269.851s" xml:id="p71" end="271.184s">可如今…</p>
      <p begin="271.892s" xml:id="p72" end="276.559s">慘被楊延嗣殺害，含冤而死</p>
      <p begin="277.224s" xml:id="p73" end="281.392s">望聖上為臣妾主持公道</p>
      <p begin="281.6s" xml:id="p74" end="282.6s">聖上</p>
      <p begin="283.934s" xml:id="p75" end="286.809s">潘豹之死實屬意外</p>
      <p begin="295.725s" xml:id="p76" end="297.059s">請聖上明察</p>
      <p begin="298.434s" xml:id="p77" end="300.6s">郡主當日並不在場</p>
      <p begin="300.851s" xml:id="p78" end="303.6s">卻斷言潘豹死於意外</p>
      <p begin="304.892s" xml:id="p79" end="306.684s">空口無憑</p>
      <p begin="306.809s" xml:id="p80" end="310.35s">只怕是有意偏袒楊家吧</p>
      <p begin="311.434s" xml:id="p81" end="314.224s">擂台比武，生死各安天命</p>
      <p begin="314.225s" xml:id="p82" end="317.392s">只怪你潘豹無福成為本郡主的駙馬</p>
      <p begin="317.434s" xml:id="p83" end="319.143s">報</p>
      <p begin="322.809s" xml:id="p84" end="325.059s">啟稟聖上，遼兵南下</p>
      <p begin="325.101s" xml:id="p85" end="329.392s">京城以北三百里處烽火臺狼煙滾滾</p>
      <p begin="330.143s" xml:id="p86" end="331.308s">遼國</p>
      <p begin="333.224s" xml:id="p87" end="335.517s">竟敢再次南侵？</p>
      <p begin="340.059s" xml:id="p88" end="341.184s">朕要下去</p>
      <p begin="349.267s" xml:id="p89" end="350.224s">聖上</p>
      <p begin="350.767s" xml:id="p90" end="352.308s">依狼煙之勢看來</p>
      <p begin="352.35s" xml:id="p91" end="354.392s">塞外敵軍數以萬計</p>
      <p begin="355.059s" xml:id="p92" end="356.934s">遼兵來勢洶洶</p>
      <p begin="359.017s" xml:id="p93" end="361.434s">遼國此次派何人出戰？</p>
      <p begin="362.35s" xml:id="p94" end="363.475s">啟秉聖上</p>
      <p begin="363.517s" xml:id="p95" end="367.392s">前方來報，遼國一員少將耶律原</p>
      <p begin="368.059s" xml:id="p96" end="370.642s">朕記得十年以前就有一位耶律將軍</p>
      <p begin="370.934s" xml:id="p97" end="371.892s">楊業</p>
      <p begin="372.059s" xml:id="p98" end="374.308s">他不是死在你的關刀之下了嗎？</p>
      <p begin="374.725s" xml:id="p99" end="376.976s">那麼今天的這個耶律原又是何人？</p>
      <p begin="377.809s" xml:id="p100" end="379.059s">回聖上</p>
      <p begin="379.267s" xml:id="p101" end="382.35s">耶律原正是這位耶律將軍之子</p>
      <p begin="382.434s" xml:id="p102" end="385.809s">此人能征善戰，英勇過人</p>
      <p begin="385.851s" xml:id="p103" end="388.225s">堪稱遼國第一猛帥</p>
      <p begin="391.559s" xml:id="p104" end="393.143s">楊業聽旨</p>
      <p begin="393.517s" xml:id="p105" end="396.059s">朕命你率六萬精兵即刻出戰</p>
      <p begin="396.976s" xml:id="p106" end="398.517s">阻止遼兵進犯</p>
      <p begin="399.6s" xml:id="p107" end="400.684s">聖上</p>
      <p begin="401.434s" xml:id="p108" end="405.017s">大宋不光只有楊業能領兵出征吧？</p>
      <p begin="406.225s" xml:id="p109" end="407.267s">聖上</p>
      <p begin="407.809s" xml:id="p110" end="411.559s">微臣甘願為主帥，出征抗敵</p>
      <p begin="412.017s" xml:id="p111" end="415.684s">也算是了卻我兒為國盡忠之遺願</p>
      <p begin="426.642s" xml:id="p112" end="427.559s">好</p>
      <p begin="429.475s" xml:id="p113" end="433.267s">潘仁美聽旨，朕封你為正統帥</p>
      <p begin="433.35s" xml:id="p114" end="435.517s">領軍六萬出師迎敵</p>
      <p begin="436.224s" xml:id="p115" end="437.976s">臣領旨</p>
      <p begin="438.559s" xml:id="p116" end="439.767s">楊業聽旨</p>
      <p begin="440.6s" xml:id="p117" end="442.267s">朕任命你為先鋒</p>
      <p begin="442.684s" xml:id="p118" end="445.059s">協助潘國丈殺退遼兵</p>
      <p begin="445.559s" xml:id="p119" end="447.224s">臣領旨</p>
      <p begin="497.684s" xml:id="p120" end="498.767s">錯了</p>
      <p begin="499.059s" xml:id="p121" end="501.976s">此戰我是先鋒，並非元帥</p>
      <p begin="505.392s" xml:id="p122" end="507.475s">我去換…</p>
      <p begin="515.517s" xml:id="p123" end="517.517s">夫人不必太過擔心</p>
      <p begin="518.976s" xml:id="p124" end="521.143s">我不是怕你體力不支</p>
      <p begin="521.809s" xml:id="p125" end="524.475s">是擔心此戰變數太大</p>
      <p begin="525.809s" xml:id="p126" end="529.559s">敵方耶律原，盟方潘仁美</p>
      <p begin="530.143s" xml:id="p127" end="533.809s">一個是仇人，一個是對頭</p>
      <p begin="533.851s" xml:id="p128" end="534.976s">夫人放心</p>
      <p begin="535.475s" xml:id="p129" end="538.224s">我對戰遼國多年未曾一敗</p>
      <p begin="538.809s" xml:id="p130" end="540.434s">至於說到潘國丈</p>
      <p begin="540.725s" xml:id="p131" end="542.267s">我二人目標一致</p>
      <p begin="542.35s" xml:id="p132" end="544.934s">我會竭盡全力阻止遼軍進犯</p>
      <p begin="544.976s" xml:id="p133" end="546.809s">共保護大宋江山</p>
      <p begin="581.809s" xml:id="p134" end="583.6s">只怕爹力不從心</p>
      <p begin="587.517s" xml:id="p135" end="588.517s">五弟放心</p>
      <p begin="589.642s" xml:id="p136" end="591.225s">爹對遼軍從未輸過</p>
      <p begin="591.392s" xml:id="p137" end="594.017s">這次也不例外，必能凱旋歸來</p>
      <p begin="594.684s" xml:id="p138" end="596.017s">爹應該讓我出戰</p>
      <p begin="596.308s" xml:id="p139" end="598.725s">不就是出任先鋒嗎？我可以</p>
      <p begin="599.6s" xml:id="p140" end="601.101s">打仗不是打擂台</p>
      <p begin="601.684s" xml:id="p141" end="604.059s">你見過大刀劈在身上鮮血四濺嗎？</p>
      <p begin="605.224s" xml:id="p142" end="607.184s">你聽過清脆的骨裂聲嗎？</p>
      <p begin="608.267s" xml:id="p143" end="609.267s">你知道…</p>
      <p begin="609.475s" xml:id="p144" end="611.976s">你的同伴、敵人一個個死在你身邊</p>
      <p begin="612.017s" xml:id="p145" end="613.267s">是甚麼感覺嗎？</p>
      <p begin="614.809s" xml:id="p146" end="617.434s">打仗…你根本甚麼都不懂</p>
      <p begin="621.684s" xml:id="p147" end="623.642s">潘仁美根本不懂調兵遣將</p>
      <p begin="624.267s" xml:id="p148" end="625.517s">只會害了爹</p>
      <p begin="629.767s" xml:id="p149" end="631.308s">父親出征在即</p>
      <p begin="631.392s" xml:id="p150" end="632.767s">該做的你們都做了</p>
      <p begin="633.224s" xml:id="p151" end="634.559s">還留在馬棚做甚麼？</p>
      <p begin="637.184s" xml:id="p152" end="638.517s">剛才那些話</p>
      <p begin="639.475s" xml:id="p153" end="641.559s">以後我不想再聽到</p>
      <p begin="642.434s" xml:id="p154" end="643.892s">是，大哥</p>
      <p begin="688.184s" xml:id="p155" end="689.224s">起來吧</p>
      <p begin="706.017s" xml:id="p156" end="706.976s">還痛嗎？</p>
      <p begin="707.892s" xml:id="p157" end="709.767s">爹，不必擔心</p>
      <p begin="709.809s" xml:id="p158" end="711.143s">五哥的藥特別管用</p>
      <p begin="753.934s" xml:id="p159" end="756.35s">這麼多年了，還是這樣合身</p>
      <p begin="799.684s" xml:id="p160" end="801.475s">楊業這樣大年紀</p>
      <p begin="801.517s" xml:id="p161" end="802.809s">還這樣能打？</p>
      <p begin="820.017s" xml:id="p162" end="822.308s">遼兵來了</p>
      <p begin="822.809s" xml:id="p163" end="823.892s">有埋伏</p>
      <p begin="826.851s" xml:id="p164" end="828.059s">馬上撤兵</p>
      <p begin="828.6s" xml:id="p165" end="829.475s">那楊先鋒…</p>
      <p begin="829.517s" xml:id="p166" end="832.143s">撤回寰州，重整兵馬</p>
      <p begin="832.225s" xml:id="p167" end="833.725s">改日再戰</p>
      <p begin="834.392s" xml:id="p168" end="836.059s">退兵</p>
      <p begin="841.184s" xml:id="p169" end="845.225s">潘仁美退兵了…</p>
      <p begin="856.767s" xml:id="p170" end="858.684s">蕭風，去</p>
      <p begin="859.101s" xml:id="p171" end="860.934s">讓老頭子吃一點苦頭</p>
      <p begin="871.559s" xml:id="p172" end="874.6s">夫人，你又做惡夢了？</p>
      <p begin="877.35s" xml:id="p173" end="878.517s">排風</p>
      <p begin="879.6s" xml:id="p174" end="882.017s">隨我去見鬼谷先生</p>
      <p begin="888.434s" xml:id="p175" end="889.934s">令公，有暗箭</p>
      <p begin="900.184s" xml:id="p176" end="901.224s">救令公</p>
      <p begin="921.308s" xml:id="p177" end="923.059s">令公，上馬</p>
      <p begin="934.767s" xml:id="p178" end="937.184s">遼軍退兵了…</p>
      <p begin="937.224s" xml:id="p179" end="938.392s">去兩狼山，走</p>
      <p begin="938.6s" xml:id="p180" end="939.851s">去兩狼山</p>
      <p begin="942.017s" xml:id="p181" end="943.475s">我是真的看不懂</p>
      <p begin="943.642s" xml:id="p182" end="944.559s">將軍</p>
      <p begin="944.6s" xml:id="p183" end="948.184s">為甚麼不將這班楞頭青一概踏平？</p>
      <p begin="951.517s" xml:id="p184" end="955.684s">總得給他們留一個能回去報信的吧</p>
      <p begin="972.642s" xml:id="p185" end="975.35s">夫人，請留步</p>
      <p begin="976.475s" xml:id="p186" end="979.308s">先生，我有事相求</p>
      <p begin="980.851s" xml:id="p187" end="983.6s">楊家保家為國</p>
      <p begin="983.725s" xml:id="p188" end="985.35s">誠不得已</p>
      <p begin="985.976s" xml:id="p189" end="989.392s">但眾生皆平等</p>
      <p begin="990.308s" xml:id="p190" end="993.851s">生命終究為生命</p>
      <p begin="994.308s" xml:id="p191" end="997.308s">此戰，令公是福是禍</p>
      <p begin="997.35s" xml:id="p192" end="999.143s">請先生明言</p>
      <p begin="999.642s" xml:id="p193" end="1003.143s">戰爭乃致禍根源</p>
      <p begin="1004.934s" xml:id="p194" end="1009.642s">楊家又福從何來？</p>
      <p begin="1012.559s" xml:id="p195" end="1013.642s">夫人</p>
      <p begin="1015.184s" xml:id="p196" end="1016.6s">請回吧</p>
      <p begin="1016.642s" xml:id="p197" end="1019.517s">先生，可有積福之法？</p>
      <p begin="1032.434s" xml:id="p198" end="1033.308s">夫人</p>
      <p begin="1033.6s" xml:id="p199" end="1035.809s">我們回去，一問究竟</p>
      <p begin="1037.224s" xml:id="p200" end="1039.559s">先生不願透露玄機</p>
      <p begin="1040.101s" xml:id="p201" end="1042.225s">我們不好強人所難</p>
      <p begin="1045.017s" xml:id="p202" end="1046.184s">夫人留步</p>
      <p begin="1048.934s" xml:id="p203" end="1050.559s">這是先生交給您的</p>
      <p begin="1060.308s" xml:id="p204" end="1061.892s">夫人，先生怎樣說？</p>
      <p begin="1066.475s" xml:id="p205" end="1068.017s">到山下等我</p>
      <p begin="1070.725s" xml:id="p206" end="1071.6s">是</p>
      <p begin="1103.059s" xml:id="p207" end="1104.684s">忍一忍…</p>
      <p begin="1106.767s" xml:id="p208" end="1108.6s">夫人…</p>
      <p begin="1118.934s" xml:id="p209" end="1120.725s">夫人…</p>
      <p begin="1127.934s" xml:id="p210" end="1129.184s">娘</p>
      <p begin="1129.224s" xml:id="p211" end="1130.101s">娘</p>
      <p begin="1151.934s" xml:id="p212" end="1152.809s">娘</p>
      <p begin="1157.017s" xml:id="p213" end="1157.976s">延平</p>
      <p begin="1161.392s" xml:id="p214" end="1163.101s">娘有話對你說</p>
      <p begin="1171.684s" xml:id="p215" end="1174.6s">（當知天命難違）</p>
      <p begin="1174.642s" xml:id="p216" end="1177.559s">（七子去六子回）</p>
      <p begin="1180.642s" xml:id="p217" end="1184.517s">娘，孩兒知道此行不同以往</p>
      <p begin="1185.767s" xml:id="p218" end="1187.017s">但是請娘放心</p>
      <p begin="1187.475s" xml:id="p219" end="1189.225s">我一定把爹救回來</p>
      <p begin="1189.267s" xml:id="p220" end="1191.517s">必保眾兄弟平安歸來</p>
      <p begin="1197.143s" xml:id="p221" end="1200.559s">如果，鬼谷先生真的言中</p>
      <p begin="1201.059s" xml:id="p222" end="1204.392s">我們七子必有一死，那就讓我來吧</p>
      <p begin="1205.6s" xml:id="p223" end="1208.559s">娘相信，相信你</p>
      <p begin="1209.809s" xml:id="p224" end="1211.517s">娘，請您發令</p>
      <p begin="1212.101s" xml:id="p225" end="1213.809s">我們立刻去營救爹</p>
      <p begin="1215.976s" xml:id="p226" end="1220.976s">為免負上欺君之罪，要獲皇上恩准</p>
      <p begin="1221.475s" xml:id="p227" end="1225.35s">為娘要親自入宮面聖</p>
      <p begin="1264.225s" xml:id="p228" end="1266.35s">暴雷，你要乖</p>
      <p begin="1266.851s" xml:id="p229" end="1268.392s">一定要助我救爹回來</p>
      <p begin="1273.017s" xml:id="p230" end="1275.642s">六弟和七弟都是首次上戰場</p>
      <p begin="1276.725s" xml:id="p231" end="1279.434s">告訴你的兩個兄弟要好好照顧他們</p>
      <p begin="1360.809s" xml:id="p232" end="1361.892s">延昭</p>
      <p begin="1379.684s" xml:id="p233" end="1380.851s">平安回來</p>
      <p begin="1394.934s" xml:id="p234" end="1396.101s">別等我了</p>
      <p begin="1408.059s" xml:id="p235" end="1409.475s">我一定等你回來</p>
      <p begin="1425.225s" xml:id="p236" end="1427.767s">娘，聖上恩准了嗎？</p>
      <p begin="1436.017s" xml:id="p237" end="1437.475s">救爹回來</p>
      <p begin="1448.059s" xml:id="p238" end="1449.767s">娘，你放心</p>
      <p begin="1471.143s" xml:id="p239" end="1472.934s">少吃檳榔</p>
      <p begin="1480.35s" xml:id="p240" end="1481.267s">娘</p>
      <p begin="1492.6s" xml:id="p241" end="1494.017s">娘…</p>
      <p begin="1497.267s" xml:id="p242" end="1501.224s">路上，要聽大哥的話</p>
      <p begin="1505.725s" xml:id="p243" end="1506.934s">起來吧</p>
      <p begin="1511.35s" xml:id="p244" end="1512.35s">出發</p>
      <p begin="1624.517s" xml:id="p245" end="1625.392s">跟著我</p>
      <p begin="1825.851s" xml:id="p246" end="1827.143s">耶律將軍</p>
      <p begin="1827.725s" xml:id="p247" end="1829.725s">若是我沒有猜錯的話</p>
      <p begin="1829.892s" xml:id="p248" end="1831.434s">你留楊業一命</p>
      <p begin="1831.559s" xml:id="p249" end="1833.725s">就是想引七子前來</p>
      <p begin="1833.934s" xml:id="p250" end="1834.934s">可現在呢？</p>
      <p begin="1835.35s" xml:id="p251" end="1837.642s">七子全部脫險了</p>
      <p begin="1838.434s" xml:id="p252" end="1842.517s">這事要是讓蕭太后知道，定會追究</p>
      <p begin="1842.976s" xml:id="p253" end="1844.517s">用兩百兵馬</p>
      <p begin="1846.224s" xml:id="p254" end="1851.225s">就能摸清楊家七子的本事，值得了</p>
      <p begin="1851.642s" xml:id="p255" end="1853.725s">將軍，你要明白</p>
      <p begin="1853.976s" xml:id="p256" end="1855.725s">我們的五萬人馬</p>
      <p begin="1855.934s" xml:id="p257" end="1859.475s">已經在寰州城外與宋軍對峙</p>
      <p begin="1860.642s" xml:id="p258" end="1864.35s">但此時此刻應該率軍攻城</p>
      <p begin="1864.934s" xml:id="p259" end="1867.267s">而不是在這一而再，再而三地</p>
      <p begin="1867.308s" xml:id="p260" end="1869.559s">與楊家糾纏才是</p>
      <p begin="1874.684s" xml:id="p261" end="1876.101s">滅掉楊家</p>
      <p begin="1876.143s" xml:id="p262" end="1879.225s">就等於去掉了遼國的心腹大患</p>
      <p begin="1887.308s" xml:id="p263" end="1890.267s">滅宋就指日可待</p>
      <p begin="1895.892s" xml:id="p264" end="1897.059s">朕如聞</p>
      <p begin="1897.101s" xml:id="p265" end="1900.725s">先鋒楊業獨以孤軍陷於強敵</p>
      <p begin="1900.767s" xml:id="p266" end="1902.642s">被困兩狼山城</p>
      <p begin="1903.059s" xml:id="p267" end="1905.308s">已遣楊家七子營救</p>
      <p begin="1905.35s" xml:id="p268" end="1908.892s">今特命潘仁美調派五千援兵</p>
      <p begin="1908.934s" xml:id="p269" end="1912.059s">同往相助，刻不容緩</p>
      <p begin="1913.143s" xml:id="p270" end="1914.642s">臣領旨</p>
      <p begin="1931.684s" xml:id="p271" end="1934.059s">城外軍情如何？</p>
      <p begin="1934.101s" xml:id="p272" end="1936.6s">回主帥，城外遼兵五萬</p>
      <p begin="1936.642s" xml:id="p273" end="1938.517s">正與我六萬大軍相峙</p>
      <p begin="1943.017s" xml:id="p274" end="1946.017s">筆墨伺候，我要立即回稟聖上</p>
      <p begin="1946.517s" xml:id="p275" end="1947.392s">是</p>
      <p begin="1970.017s" xml:id="p276" end="1971.35s">抓緊時間，把兵器修整好</p>
      <p begin="1971.392s" xml:id="p277" end="1972.267s">是…</p>
      <p begin="1978.017s" xml:id="p278" end="1979.225s">傷怎樣了？</p>
      <p begin="1979.475s" xml:id="p279" end="1980.392s">沒事的</p>
      <p begin="1993.184s" xml:id="p280" end="1995.35s">弟兄們，把城門加固好</p>
      <p begin="2017.767s" xml:id="p281" end="2018.767s">令公</p>
      <p begin="2020.392s" xml:id="p282" end="2021.434s">吃一點吧</p>
      <p begin="2025.224s" xml:id="p283" end="2026.517s">留給士兵吧</p>
      <p begin="2028.725s" xml:id="p284" end="2030.017s">大家都吃了</p>
      <p begin="2035.892s" xml:id="p285" end="2037.725s">你跟隨我爭戰多年</p>
      <p begin="2038.851s" xml:id="p286" end="2041.267s">論打仗，沒話說</p>
      <p begin="2042.224s" xml:id="p287" end="2045.851s">說謊？你可不在行</p>
      <p begin="2046.767s" xml:id="p288" end="2048.059s">你以為我不知道</p>
      <p begin="2048.101s" xml:id="p289" end="2051.517s">糧和水早就已經快沒了嗎？</p>
      <p begin="2056.475s" xml:id="p290" end="2057.475s">令公</p>
      <p begin="2058.143s" xml:id="p291" end="2059.851s">我跟你征戰這麼多年</p>
      <p begin="2060.35s" xml:id="p292" end="2063.224s">從未見過這麼慘的戰況</p>
      <p begin="2071.224s" xml:id="p293" end="2073.059s">可能我真的老了</p>
      <p begin="2074.976s" xml:id="p294" end="2077.101s">那麼多遼兵埋伏四周</p>
      <p begin="2077.851s" xml:id="p295" end="2080.851s">我怎麼會毫無察覺…</p>
      <p begin="2082.308s" xml:id="p296" end="2084.976s">耶律原為甚麼還不攻城？</p>
      <p begin="2091.809s" xml:id="p297" end="2094.6s">楊家軍來了…</p>
      <p begin="2122.184s" xml:id="p298" end="2123.392s">爹…</p>
      <p begin="2123.434s" xml:id="p299" end="2125.224s">孩兒來遲　　爹…</p>
      <p begin="2125.267s" xml:id="p300" end="2126.559s">害爹受苦了</p>
      <p begin="2126.6s" xml:id="p301" end="2128.767s">兩狼山城已被遼軍包圍</p>
      <p begin="2129.225s" xml:id="p302" end="2130.934s">你們怎麼能夠闖進來的？</p>
      <p begin="2132.517s" xml:id="p303" end="2134.434s">爹，你不必疑慮</p>
      <p begin="2134.475s" xml:id="p304" end="2136.6s">我等只是稍稍變換陣勢</p>
      <p begin="2136.767s" xml:id="p305" end="2138.35s">就讓遼賊措手不及</p>
      <p begin="2138.559s" xml:id="p306" end="2140.392s">輕而易舉地便殺了進來</p>
      <p begin="2142.434s" xml:id="p307" end="2144.143s">令公…　　爹…</p>
      <p begin="2144.184s" xml:id="p308" end="2145.767s">中計了</p>
      <p begin="2151.517s" xml:id="p309" end="2152.809s">十年前</p>
      <p begin="2153.184s" xml:id="p310" end="2156.267s">我宋軍大敗遼國三十萬大軍</p>
      <p begin="2157.184s" xml:id="p311" end="2160.392s">耶律將軍所帶兵馬無一生還</p>
      <p begin="2161.35s" xml:id="p312" end="2165.434s">現在，他的兒子耶律原留我一命</p>
      <p begin="2165.851s" xml:id="p313" end="2168.642s">就是要引你們前來報仇的</p>
      <p begin="2171.392s" xml:id="p314" end="2174.225s">爹，我現在必須把箭拔出來</p>
      <p begin="2176.225s" xml:id="p315" end="2177.475s">延平</p>
      <p begin="2178.059s" xml:id="p316" end="2180.101s">馬上帶弟弟們離開兩狼山</p>
      <p begin="2180.475s" xml:id="p317" end="2183.017s">爹，難道你不離開嗎？</p>
      <p begin="2184.559s" xml:id="p318" end="2186.434s">我馳騁疆場這麼多年</p>
      <p begin="2187.434s" xml:id="p319" end="2189.101s">從來沒有畏懼過</p>
      <p begin="2190.35s" xml:id="p320" end="2193.101s">難道如今卻要當個逃兵嗎？</p>
      <p begin="2193.308s" xml:id="p321" end="2196.725s">爹，潘仁美的救兵日落就能趕到</p>
      <p begin="2197.35s" xml:id="p322" end="2199.559s">我們先守城，等援軍到了</p>
      <p begin="2199.6s" xml:id="p323" end="2201.809s">我們兄弟幾個一起殺出去</p>
      <p begin="2202.392s" xml:id="p324" end="2203.392s">要救</p>
      <p begin="2203.6s" xml:id="p325" end="2205.267s">早在金沙灘就救了</p>
      <p begin="2206.017s" xml:id="p326" end="2207.308s">他若肯出兵</p>
      <p begin="2207.35s" xml:id="p327" end="2209.308s">我們也不會落得今天這個地步</p>
      <p begin="2210.642s" xml:id="p328" end="2212.934s">如今他兵都撤了</p>
      <p begin="2212.976s" xml:id="p329" end="2214.809s">怎麼可能再回來送死？</p>
      <p begin="2216.851s" xml:id="p330" end="2218.392s">潘仁美這個老賊</p>
      <p begin="2218.809s" xml:id="p331" end="2221.017s">除非有人拿刀架在他脖子上逼他</p>
      <p begin="2221.101s" xml:id="p332" end="2223.224s">否則，他絕不會冒險</p>
      <p begin="2225.101s" xml:id="p333" end="2227.976s">爹，此行是聖上恩准的</p>
      <p begin="2235.267s" xml:id="p334" end="2238.684s">難得聖上還惦記著楊業</p>
      <p begin="2240.184s" xml:id="p335" end="2241.725s">都怪楊業無能</p>
      <p begin="2242.392s" xml:id="p336" end="2245.35s">未能替聖上守住疆土</p>
      <p begin="2252.642s" xml:id="p337" end="2254.559s">延平，時間不多了</p>
      <p begin="2254.6s" xml:id="p338" end="2256.725s">快帶弟弟們離開兩狼山</p>
      <p begin="2256.851s" xml:id="p339" end="2258.101s">爹…　　令公</p>
      <p begin="2258.559s" xml:id="p340" end="2259.434s">令公</p>
      <p begin="2260.267s" xml:id="p341" end="2261.224s">呼延將軍</p>
      <p begin="2261.559s" xml:id="p342" end="2262.934s">兩狼山另有出路嗎？</p>
      <p begin="2262.976s" xml:id="p343" end="2265.517s">有是有，可是路途險惡</p>
      <p begin="2266.308s" xml:id="p344" end="2268.017s">那根本會算不上一條路</p>
      <p begin="2268.059s" xml:id="p345" end="2269.642s">快走</p>
      <p begin="2269.934s" xml:id="p346" end="2271.35s">請爹相信孩兒們</p>
      <p begin="2271.392s" xml:id="p347" end="2273.017s">定能帶爹離開兩狼山</p>
      <p begin="2274.017s" xml:id="p348" end="2276.059s">我無心再走了</p>
      <p begin="2277.809s" xml:id="p349" end="2278.851s">爹</p>
      <p begin="2279.559s" xml:id="p350" end="2280.809s">你可以不走</p>
      <p begin="2281.767s" xml:id="p351" end="2283.809s">也可以跟耶律原決一死戰</p>
      <p begin="2285.225s" xml:id="p352" end="2286.35s">但卻不能讓一支箭</p>
      <p begin="2286.392s" xml:id="p353" end="2288.225s">將自己困在這裏等死</p>
      <p begin="2291.143s" xml:id="p354" end="2292.224s">呼延將軍</p>
      <p begin="2292.392s" xml:id="p355" end="2293.267s">請給我們帶路</p>
      <p begin="2293.308s" xml:id="p356" end="2294.224s">好</p>
      <p begin="2294.225s" xml:id="p357" end="2297.101s">七弟、六弟，守在這裏</p>
      <p begin="2297.267s" xml:id="p358" end="2298.184s">是</p>
      <p begin="2298.224s" xml:id="p359" end="2299.684s">五弟，快把爹治好</p>
      <p begin="2301.559s" xml:id="p360" end="2302.434s">走</p>
      <p begin="2312.308s" xml:id="p361" end="2314.725s">爹，我要拔箭了</p>
      <p begin="2318.6s" xml:id="p362" end="2320.767s">別碰，箭上有毒</p>
      <p begin="2327.517s" xml:id="p363" end="2328.809s">毒已入骨</p>
      <p begin="2330.434s" xml:id="p364" end="2331.35s">爹</p>
      <p begin="2333.6s" xml:id="p365" end="2335.143s">我幫你刮骨取毒</p>
      <p begin="2381.143s" xml:id="p366" end="2383.184s">爹，都是孩兒的錯</p>
      <p begin="2383.934s" xml:id="p367" end="2385.267s">孩兒這就去寰州城</p>
      <p begin="2385.35s" xml:id="p368" end="2386.475s">逼潘仁美出兵</p>
      <p begin="2388.184s" xml:id="p369" end="2389.059s">爹</p>
      <p begin="2389.851s" xml:id="p370" end="2391.143s">六弟，去追</p>
