      <p begin="3048.559s" xml:id="p406" end="3049.642s">突襲不成</p>
      <p begin="3049.684s" xml:id="p407" end="3050.851s">圍剿不得</p>
      <p begin="3051.225s" xml:id="p408" end="3055.225s">看來將軍還真不是楊家的對手</p>
      <p begin="3055.684s" xml:id="p409" end="3056.934s">既然如此</p>
      <p begin="3057.143s" xml:id="p410" end="3059.892s">那就速速返回寰州城戰線</p>
      <p begin="3061.017s" xml:id="p411" end="3064.559s">如若不然，我就向蕭太后如實稟告</p>
      <p begin="3068.976s" xml:id="p412" end="3070.017s">去</p>
      <p begin="3070.517s" xml:id="p413" end="3071.976s">稟告蕭太后</p>
      <p begin="3072.517s" xml:id="p414" end="3077.059s">監軍大人英勇陣亡、為國捐軀</p>
      <p begin="3077.267s" xml:id="p415" end="3078.184s">是</p>
      <p begin="3082.642s" xml:id="p416" end="3084.184s">立即召集一百精騎</p>
      <p begin="3084.224s" xml:id="p417" end="3085.267s">隨我去追殺楊家父子</p>
      <p begin="3085.308s" xml:id="p418" end="3086.224s">是</p>
      <p begin="3086.225s" xml:id="p419" end="3087.267s">沙斯木　　在</p>
      <p begin="3087.308s" xml:id="p420" end="3090.684s">帶其餘兵馬趕赴寰州城一線</p>
      <p begin="3090.725s" xml:id="p421" end="3092.642s">等我回來，再一舉進攻</p>
      <p begin="3092.684s" xml:id="p422" end="3093.976s">是…　　快</p>
      <p begin="3167.6s" xml:id="p423" end="3169.224s">爹，堅持住</p>
      <p begin="3204.6s" xml:id="p424" end="3205.559s">大哥</p>
      <p begin="3206.517s" xml:id="p425" end="3207.475s">對不起</p>
      <p begin="3216.224s" xml:id="p426" end="3217.559s">我們還回得去嗎？</p>
