      <p begin="3496.517s" xml:id="p468" end="3497.976s">停</p>
      <p begin="3499.725s" xml:id="p469" end="3501.308s">來者何人？</p>
      <p begin="3502.517s" xml:id="p470" end="3504.642s">我是楊家七子楊延嗣</p>
      <p begin="3505.976s" xml:id="p471" end="3509.224s">特來求見潘國丈，請開城門</p>
      <p begin="3532.725s" xml:id="p472" end="3534.017s">我爹被困兩狼山</p>
      <p begin="3534.475s" xml:id="p473" end="3536.059s">你為何不派兵營救？</p>
      <p begin="3538.059s" xml:id="p474" end="3540.517s">我實在不明白你在說甚麼</p>
      <p begin="3541.642s" xml:id="p475" end="3543.392s">你是一個遼國人</p>
      <p begin="3544.225s" xml:id="p476" end="3546.725s">潘仁美，你看清楚了</p>
      <p begin="3547.184s" xml:id="p477" end="3549.851s">我是楊家七子楊延嗣</p>
      <p begin="3561.684s" xml:id="p478" end="3562.767s">潘國丈</p>
      <p begin="3563.6s" xml:id="p479" end="3566.6s">我這次來，就沒有打算活著回去</p>
