      <p begin="3672.892s" xml:id="p490" end="3673.934s">爹</p>
      <p begin="3700.475s" xml:id="p491" end="3702.934s">楊業，你找我嗎？</p>
      <p begin="3705.851s" xml:id="p492" end="3707.225s">找我何事</p>
      <p begin="3709.642s" xml:id="p493" end="3710.892s">蘇武大人</p>
      <p begin="3712.143s" xml:id="p494" end="3714.392s">你有沒有看到我家延嗣？</p>
      <p begin="3715.6s" xml:id="p495" end="3718.684s">老七？已經走了</p>
      <p begin="3719.225s" xml:id="p496" end="3720.308s">他去哪裏了？</p>
      <p begin="3720.934s" xml:id="p497" end="3722.725s">是否可以帶我去找他？</p>
      <p begin="3723.642s" xml:id="p498" end="3725.851s">楊業，你看看</p>
      <p begin="3726.934s" xml:id="p499" end="3728.684s">我這隻老羊</p>
      <p begin="3730.35s" xml:id="p500" end="3733.892s">它瘸成這樣，還是走個不停</p>
      <p begin="3734.184s" xml:id="p501" end="3738.143s">看它這個樣子，定是受過重傷</p>
      <p begin="3739.184s" xml:id="p502" end="3741.143s">不知是怎麼活下來的？</p>
      <p begin="3741.184s" xml:id="p503" end="3744.224s">活？活不了</p>
      <p begin="3744.267s" xml:id="p504" end="3747.684s">今日，老羊必死</p>
      <p begin="3755.101s" xml:id="p505" end="3757.767s">你看，這是甚麼？</p>
