      <p begin="3838.517s" xml:id="p521" end="3839.392s">夫人</p>
      <p begin="3839.434s" xml:id="p522" end="3840.475s">八賢王求見</p>
      <p begin="3848.308s" xml:id="p523" end="3852.642s">夫人，潘國丈上書聖上</p>
      <p begin="3852.851s" xml:id="p524" end="3855.851s">因寰州城戰況危急</p>
      <p begin="3855.892s" xml:id="p525" end="3858.143s">未能調派援軍</p>
      <p begin="3858.684s" xml:id="p526" end="3860.642s">令公與七子呢？</p>
      <p begin="3860.809s" xml:id="p527" end="3862.809s">生死未卜</p>
      <p begin="3870.892s" xml:id="p528" end="3873.475s">多謝八賢王前來報信</p>
      <p begin="3875.267s" xml:id="p529" end="3879.224s">那老朽先行告退了</p>
      <p begin="3880.35s" xml:id="p530" end="3883.517s">排風，送八賢王</p>
      <p begin="3919.224s" xml:id="p531" end="3922.101s">五弟，快把爹治好…</p>
      <p begin="3929.725s" xml:id="p532" end="3930.767s">怎麼會？</p>
      <p begin="3934.517s" xml:id="p533" end="3935.6s">爹</p>
      <p begin="3982.308s" xml:id="p534" end="3983.851s">我要帶爹回家</p>
      <p begin="3988.225s" xml:id="p535" end="3989.6s">我要帶爹回家</p>
      <p begin="3993.642s" xml:id="p536" end="3995.143s">娘還等著爹的</p>
      <p begin="4052.017s" xml:id="p537" end="4052.892s">大哥</p>
      <p begin="4053.517s" xml:id="p538" end="4054.517s">追兵已到</p>
      <p begin="4055.851s" xml:id="p539" end="4057.143s">我們要不要出去迎戰？</p>
      <p begin="4058.767s" xml:id="p540" end="4060.143s">帶爹回家要緊</p>
      <p begin="4119.684s" xml:id="p541" end="4120.934s">剛剛離開</p>
      <p begin="4122.017s" xml:id="p542" end="4123.143s">有多少人馬？</p>
      <p begin="4123.184s" xml:id="p543" end="4124.308s">不過五至六騎</p>
      <p begin="4195.392s" xml:id="p544" end="4196.434s">大哥</p>
      <p begin="4197.809s" xml:id="p545" end="4199.059s">耶律原追兵來了</p>
      <p begin="4199.767s" xml:id="p546" end="4201.059s">至少八十精騎</p>
      <p begin="4201.934s" xml:id="p547" end="4202.892s">這麼快？</p>
      <p begin="4203.809s" xml:id="p548" end="4205.517s">沒想到我們選這樣一條路</p>
      <p begin="4205.642s" xml:id="p549" end="4207.017s">也會被他們發現</p>
      <p begin="4207.225s" xml:id="p550" end="4208.809s">兩狼山我們都殺出來了</p>
      <p begin="4208.851s" xml:id="p551" end="4210.976s">不如這次我們再殺出去</p>
      <p begin="4211.767s" xml:id="p552" end="4213.809s">你們先走，我留在這裏</p>
      <p begin="4214.225s" xml:id="p553" end="4215.934s">你們保護六弟，送爹回家</p>
      <p begin="4216.684s" xml:id="p554" end="4218.184s">我來拖延遼軍時間</p>
      <p begin="4223.267s" xml:id="p555" end="4225.851s">大哥，我們都是兄弟</p>
      <p begin="4226.059s" xml:id="p556" end="4227.892s">怎麼能讓你一個人留在這裏？</p>
      <p begin="4228.267s" xml:id="p557" end="4229.308s">不行，大哥</p>
      <p begin="4229.559s" xml:id="p558" end="4232.559s">我從來沒想過帶爹回家</p>
      <p begin="4232.976s" xml:id="p559" end="4234.559s">要犧牲任何一個兄弟</p>
      <p begin="4234.934s" xml:id="p560" end="4236.017s">你們聽我說</p>
      <p begin="4237.225s" xml:id="p561" end="4238.559s">爹已經不在了</p>
      <p begin="4239.35s" xml:id="p562" end="4242.725s">兩狼山犧牲的弟兄們也回不去了</p>
      <p begin="4243.475s" xml:id="p563" end="4246.017s">可是娘在等我們</p>
      <p begin="4246.224s" xml:id="p564" end="4248.308s">家裏還有很多人等著我們回去</p>
      <p begin="4249.642s" xml:id="p565" end="4252.392s">我留在這裏，會有辦法脫身的</p>
      <p begin="4252.642s" xml:id="p566" end="4254.6s">放心吧，雁門關見</p>
      <p begin="4257.892s" xml:id="p567" end="4260.184s">大哥一個人怎麼能對付八十精騎？</p>
      <p begin="4260.225s" xml:id="p568" end="4261.184s">我留下</p>
      <p begin="4261.517s" xml:id="p569" end="4263.225s">三弟帶隊，趕往雁門關</p>
      <p begin="4263.267s" xml:id="p570" end="4265.224s">我和大哥留在這裏拖延遼軍</p>
      <p begin="4265.225s" xml:id="p571" end="4266.851s">快走…</p>
      <p begin="4275.267s" xml:id="p572" end="4276.224s">二弟</p>
      <p begin="4284.642s" xml:id="p573" end="4285.851s">這是臨行前</p>
      <p begin="4286.267s" xml:id="p574" end="4288.6s">娘從鬼谷先生那裏求來的</p>
      <p begin="4291.475s" xml:id="p575" end="4293.767s">（當知天命難違）</p>
      <p begin="4293.809s" xml:id="p576" end="4296.143s">（七子去六子回）</p>
      <p begin="4298.475s" xml:id="p577" end="4299.725s">我答應過娘</p>
      <p begin="4300.725s" xml:id="p578" end="4303.059s">必保弟弟們平安回家</p>
      <p begin="4305.6s" xml:id="p579" end="4306.517s">二弟</p>
      <p begin="4308.475s" xml:id="p580" end="4309.642s">保護好他們</p>
      <p begin="4311.475s" xml:id="p581" end="4312.976s">帶他們回去見娘</p>
      <p begin="4317.267s" xml:id="p582" end="4320.517s">大哥，我明白了</p>
      <p begin="4324.892s" xml:id="p583" end="4325.934s">雁門關見</p>
      <p begin="4463.059s" xml:id="p584" end="4464.684s">我爹戰死沙場</p>
      <p begin="4464.725s" xml:id="p585" end="4466.059s">我為他自豪</p>
      <p begin="4466.642s" xml:id="p586" end="4468.101s">怪不得你爹</p>
      <p begin="4473.392s" xml:id="p587" end="4475.559s">可我還是不能放過你們</p>
      <p begin="4478.308s" xml:id="p588" end="4481.725s">延平，你明白嗎？</p>
      <p begin="4482.434s" xml:id="p589" end="4486.434s">我不忍心看我娘整日以淚洗面</p>
      <p begin="4486.642s" xml:id="p590" end="4489.225s">連我爹的屍首都無處去尋</p>
      <p begin="4490.225s" xml:id="p591" end="4492.892s">最後含恨而終</p>
      <p begin="4496.101s" xml:id="p592" end="4499.392s">我不但要讓你爹死</p>
      <p begin="4500.559s" xml:id="p593" end="4503.434s">我還要你們兄弟幾個都死</p>
      <p begin="4504.224s" xml:id="p594" end="4506.809s">一個一個地死</p>
      <p begin="4508.517s" xml:id="p595" end="4510.101s">我要讓你娘</p>
      <p begin="4510.642s" xml:id="p596" end="4516.143s">比我娘更痛、更苦</p>
      <p begin="4517.225s" xml:id="p597" end="4519.101s">大哥</p>
      <p begin="4560.224s" xml:id="p598" end="4561.767s">大哥</p>
      <p begin="4632.559s" xml:id="p599" end="4636.892s">大哥，我不可以讓你一個人走的</p>
      <p begin="4643.559s" xml:id="p600" end="4645.559s">（當知天命難違）</p>
      <p begin="4645.6s" xml:id="p601" end="4647.6s">（七子去六子回）</p>
      <p begin="4662.35s" xml:id="p602" end="4664.517s">大龍</p>
      <p begin="4667.308s" xml:id="p603" end="4669.642s">三哥…</p>
      <p begin="4670.642s" xml:id="p604" end="4672.851s">你們先走，我接應五弟</p>
      <p begin="4672.892s" xml:id="p605" end="4674.101s">送爹回去要緊</p>
      <p begin="4680.6s" xml:id="p606" end="4681.475s">五弟</p>
      <p begin="4684.143s" xml:id="p607" end="4685.017s">來</p>
      <p begin="4698.434s" xml:id="p608" end="4699.892s">天波府楊延輝、楊延德</p>
      <p begin="4699.934s" xml:id="p609" end="4700.976s">有事相求</p>
      <p begin="4702.059s" xml:id="p610" end="4703.101s">聽命</p>
      <p begin="4752.392s" xml:id="p611" end="4754.35s">你不是常說吃檳榔無益嗎？</p>
      <p begin="4754.809s" xml:id="p612" end="4756.225s">我現在要亢奮</p>
      <p begin="4791.767s" xml:id="p613" end="4793.475s">爺爺你看，風向變了</p>
      <p begin="4903.392s" xml:id="p614" end="4904.809s">射馬不射人</p>
      <p begin="4905.017s" xml:id="p615" end="4906.517s">此人別有用心</p>
      <p begin="4907.225s" xml:id="p616" end="4908.225s">箭有毒</p>
      <p begin="4909.143s" xml:id="p617" end="4910.434s">爹中的就是這樣的箭</p>
      <p begin="4916.684s" xml:id="p618" end="4917.767s">我去把他殺了</p>
      <p begin="4919.976s" xml:id="p619" end="4921.143s">一路跟著烽火台走</p>
      <p begin="4921.184s" xml:id="p620" end="4922.225s">就可以到雁門關</p>
      <p begin="4922.642s" xml:id="p621" end="4923.767s">你一定要把爹帶回去</p>
      <p begin="4924.6s" xml:id="p622" end="4927.059s">三哥…</p>
      <p begin="5108.184s" xml:id="p623" end="5109.143s">爹</p>
      <p begin="5111.434s" xml:id="p624" end="5112.892s">我們快要到家了</p>
      <p begin="5129.017s" xml:id="p625" end="5131.224s">你是老六，還是老七？</p>
      <p begin="5139.059s" xml:id="p626" end="5140.475s">救爹回來</p>
      <p begin="5156.517s" xml:id="p627" end="5159.017s">你們楊家人真是一個不如一個</p>
      <p begin="5159.851s" xml:id="p628" end="5162.392s">前五個都死得坦坦蕩蕩的</p>
      <p begin="5162.725s" xml:id="p629" end="5165.6s">輪到你，就只會逃跑的</p>
      <p begin="5178.684s" xml:id="p630" end="5180.308s">屍首你不能帶走</p>
      <p begin="5182.559s" xml:id="p631" end="5185.267s">我要你爹和我爹同一個下場</p>
      <p begin="5187.184s" xml:id="p632" end="5189.224s">這是我對我娘的承諾</p>
      <p begin="5191.017s" xml:id="p633" end="5192.892s">我背上背的承諾</p>
      <p begin="5194.559s" xml:id="p634" end="5195.976s">比你更多</p>
      <p begin="5355.059s" xml:id="p635" end="5359.101s">我是第六個</p>
      <p begin="5361.308s" xml:id="p636" end="5362.767s">楊延昭</p>
      <p begin="5365.642s" xml:id="p637" end="5367.017s">你記住了</p>
      <p begin="5482.392s" xml:id="p638" end="5483.308s">娘</p>
      <p begin="5485.101s" xml:id="p639" end="5488.267s">我們把爹帶回來了</p>
      <p begin="5543.35s" xml:id="p640" end="5544.308s">我們…</p>
      <p begin="5545.976s" xml:id="p641" end="5547.392s">回家</p>
      <p begin="5589.725s" xml:id="p642" end="5590.934s">（耶律原死後）</p>
      <p begin="5590.976s" xml:id="p643" end="5592.224s">（遼國大軍成為無帥之師）</p>
      <p begin="5592.225s" xml:id="p644" end="5593.434s">（蕭太后無奈）</p>
      <p begin="5593.475s" xml:id="p645" end="5594.6s">（只得先從寰州城撒兵）</p>
      <p begin="5594.642s" xml:id="p646" end="5595.767s">（再作計議）</p>
      <p begin="5595.809s" xml:id="p647" end="5596.934s">（宋朝偷得片刻安寧）</p>
      <p begin="5596.976s" xml:id="p648" end="5598.101s">（潘仁美老奸巨猾、殘害忠良）</p>
      <p begin="5598.143s" xml:id="p649" end="5599.267s">（雖不被懲治）</p>
      <p begin="5599.308s" xml:id="p650" end="5600.475s">（卻換來遺臭萬年的醜名）</p>
      <p begin="5600.517s" xml:id="p651" end="5601.684s">（大郎、二郎、三郎及七郎的）</p>
      <p begin="5601.725s" xml:id="p652" end="5602.892s">（屍首被尋回）</p>
      <p begin="5602.934s" xml:id="p653" end="5604.101s">（並已送回家鄉安葬）</p>
      <p begin="5604.143s" xml:id="p654" end="5607.642s">（但四郎、五郎一直落不明）</p>
      <p begin="5607.684s" xml:id="p655" end="5608.892s">（六郎繼承楊家保家衛國的使命）</p>
      <p begin="5608.934s" xml:id="p656" end="5611.267s">（更與郡主成親）</p>
      <p begin="5611.308s" xml:id="p657" end="5613.059s">（楊家傳奇得以延續）</p>
      <p begin="5613.101s" xml:id="p658" end="5614.851s">（成為後世稱頌的對象）</p>
      <p begin="5614.892s" xml:id="p659" end="5620.434s">（楊家將亦成為）</p>
      <p begin="5620.475s" xml:id="p660" end="5626.101s">（「忠、孝、仁、義」的代表）</p>
    </div>
